      • strings_can_be_null

        @Cast(value="bool")
public boolean strings_can_be_null()
        Whether string / binary columns can have null values. If true, then strings in "null_values" are considered null for string columns. If false, then all strings are valid string values.

      • strings_can_be_null

        public ConvertOptions strings_can_be_null(boolean setter)

      • quoted_strings_can_be_null

        @Cast(value="bool")
public boolean quoted_strings_can_be_null()
        Whether quoted values can be null. If true, then strings in "null_values" are also considered null when they appear quoted in the CSV file. Otherwise, quoted values are never considered null.

      • quoted_strings_can_be_null

        public ConvertOptions quoted_strings_can_be_null(boolean setter)

      • auto_dict_encode

        @Cast(value="bool")
public boolean auto_dict_encode()
        Whether to try to automatically dict-encode string / binary data. If true, then when type inference detects a string or binary column, it is dict-encoded up to auto_dict_max_cardinality distinct values (per chunk), after which it switches to regular encoding. This setting is ignored for non-inferred columns (those in column_types).

      • auto_dict_encode

        public ConvertOptions auto_dict_encode(boolean setter)

      • include_columns

        @ByRef
public StringVector include_columns()
        If non-empty, indicates the names of columns from the CSV file that should be actually read and converted (in the vector's order). Columns not in this vector will be ignored.

      • include_columns

        public ConvertOptions include_columns(StringVector setter)

      • include_missing_columns

        @Cast(value="bool")
public boolean include_missing_columns()
        If false, columns in include_columns but not in the CSV file will error out. If true, columns in include_columns but not in the CSV file will produce a column of nulls (whose type is selected using column_types, or null by default) This option is ignored if include_columns is empty.

      • include_missing_columns

        public ConvertOptions include_missing_columns(boolean setter)
